a.n: Agent Binky: Pets of the Universe I (18)

p.k: Ice Cream Shuttle An alien (code name: bee) goes in the window of the Ice Cream Shuttle (code name: ice cream truck) and the team is on a mission to take back the shuttle.
p.d: Binky is an indoor cat who is a member of a secret agency. Teamed with like-minded pet agents, they are on a mission to keep their humans and "space station" safe from "aliens".
